#26700
The Geometry of Shadows~
The Babylon Project was our last, best hope for peace. A self-contained
world five miles long, located in neutral territory. A place of commerce
and diplomacy for a quarter of a million humans and aliens. A shining
beacon in space, all alone in the night. It was the dawn of the Third
Age of Mankind... the year the Great War came upon us all. This is the
last of the Babylon stations. The year is 2259. The name of the place is
Babylon 5.
~
