#26702
Upper Level of Observation Dome~
When it is quiet, with no ships departing or approaching the station, an 
observer can look out through the curved windows and see the stars glowing
silently against the black backdrop of space. At times like these it might
be possible to contemplate teh infinity of the cosmos and wonder at your
place in the universe.
