#26703
{BOL}{YEL}Entering Yellow Sector{yel}~
Located aft of the Grey Sector and the carousel, Yellow Sector does not
rotate. It contains the variable-g research labs as well as the primary
fusion core and the associated subsystems. Cooling fins run the length
of the sector, located on the outside of the hull.
~
