#26705
{BOL}{RED}Entering Red Sector{red}~
Red Sector is the main marketplace and business area. Together with
service facilities such as Medlab 1, the Judicary, Security Central,
and the holding cells, the principal areas of note here include the
Zocalo, hotel suites, casinos, bars, legal brothels, and stores of
all types. Red Sector is a public area. Civilian access is granted
at all times.
~
