#26709
{BOL}{GRE}Top of Main Administration Block{gre}~
From a height of three stories you can see the entire length of the
carousel section. The Park, Trees, and streams, the river, the parkland,
the hedge maze, the Zen Garden, the sports fields, the Rotunda, the
Mosque. Twelve square miles of parkland wrapped into a hollow cylinder
a mile and a half in diameter.
~
